of established convention.\\n\\n## Correct Reuse Observed\\n\\nThe diff correctly reuses:\\n- The `settings.IsXxxEnabled` pattern for the new `IsExternalAgentsEnabled`\\n- The `agent.Register` / `agent.Get` / `agent.List` registry API\\n- The `paths.WorktreeRoot` utility for repo root resolution\\n- The `logging.Debug` structured logging throughout discovery\\n- The `agent.Event` and `agent.HookInput` domain types (not reinvented)\\n\\n## Summary\\n\\nZero real code reuse issues found. No existing functionality was duplicated. No hand-rolled patterns replaced existing helpers. Every new function serves a purpose not covered by existing utilities. The only arguable duplication (the 7 As* helpers) is a deliberate readability-over-DRY tradeoff that I consider reasonable.\\n\\nThe review file would be at: `/Users/nodo/work/cli/docs/requirements/external-plugins/review-03.md`. Please grant Write permission if you would like me to persist it to disk.</result>\\n<usage><total_tokens>85850</total_tokens><tool_uses>43</tool_uses><duration_ms>189713</duration_ms></usage>\\n</task-notification>\\nFull transcript available at: /private/tmp/claude-501/-Users-nodo-work-cli/tasks/a541277b90d03618d.output\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"d2a4cc48-e726-4311-8854-2496b7ba5d37\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/nodo/work/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"c1c82db1-4d21-4b6d-a10b-102dd81b7406\",\"version\":\"2.1.69\",\"gitBranch\":\"nodo/external-plugins\",\"slug\":\"delightful-booping-dahl\",\"type\":\"user\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_01CergvrULTSPfT6hizxtYAk\",\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"<retrieval_status>timeout</retrieval_status>\"}]},\"uuid\":\"2381e469-8f10-46ab-849d-18746ab4b470\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-05T10:24:36.439Z\",\"toolUseResult\":{\"retrieval_status\":\"timeout\",\"task\":null},\"sourceToolAssistantUUID\":\"d2a4cc48-e726-4311-8854-2496b7ba5d37\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"2381e469-8f10-46ab-849d-18746ab4b470\",\"i